Write a query to display the order id and customer id of all
the orders placed in the month of 'APRIL'. Sort the result set based on customer id in ascending order and order id in descending order.

(HINT : Retrieve data from Orders table. Data is Case Sensitive)




select Order_id,Cust_id 
from Orders
where month(Order_date)=04
order by Cust_id asc,Order_id desc;
